					<p class="byline">by <a class="byline-author" href="/editor/tateru-nino">Tateru Nino</a> <a href="http://massively.joystiq.com/editor/tateru-nino/rss.xml"><img src="http://www.blogsmithmedia.com/massively.joystiq.com/media/writer_rss.gif" /></a> (5 months ago)</p>

